sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as NguoiDungDaDangNhap
participant Client as UngDungWeb
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant AuthMW as Middleware_XacThuc
participant PermMW as Middleware_PhanQuyen
participant RoleSvc as RolePermissionService
participant Domain as DichVuDich

Note over User,Domain: Chặng 1 - Luồng cho phép
User->>Client: Thao tác API private
Client->>Gateway: Request kèm JWT
Gateway->>AuthMW: Verify token
AuthMW-->>Gateway: Hợp lệ
Gateway->>PermMW: Map action theo route
PermMW->>RoleSvc: POST /api/permissions/check
RoleSvc-->>PermMW: allowed=true
PermMW-->>Gateway: pass
Gateway->>Domain: Proxy request
Domain-->>Client: 2xx thành công
